---
title: Pan-Roasted Chicken with Dijon Mushroom Sauce and Israeli Couscous
description: Chicken gets a major flavour upgrade when Dijon mustard is involved. In fact, it’s one of our secret weapons in the kitchen. This condiment pairs impeccably with garlic and lemon to lend a distinct and rich flavor to the sauce.
